      "span_text": "Polymerase chain reaction (PCR) primers LCO 1490 (59GGTCAACAAATCATAAAGATATTGG 39) and HCO 2198 (59TAAACTTCAGGGTGACCAAAAAATCA 39; [CITATION_1] were used to obtain sequences from the Folmer Region of the COI gene."
